{"tid":1654324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊實現《五大訴求》《真實雙普選》路線圖 反對《緊急法》入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-14T14:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T20:47:21.000Z","uid":260023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a09808f2f3254f719bf179fb9579e0ed582dde5","tid":1654324,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"幫我推一下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊</span>實現<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《五大訴求》[</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《真實雙普選》</span></span>路線圖 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反對《緊急法》</span></span>入嚟<br />\n  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.一條殖民地惡法 ，只有<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港督</span></span>根據英國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">憲制授權行使</span></span>《緊急情況規例條例》</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《中英聯合聲明》《基本法》 </span></span>完全<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有授權特首</span></span>可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">行使抵觸</span></span>《基本法》的《緊急情況規例條例》<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.追究反對</span></span>特區政府破壞《中英聯合聲明》 引用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 抵觸</span></span>《基本法》 的 《緊急情況規例條例》 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">破壞《中英聯合聲明》《基本法》《立法會議事規則》《香港法律》</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我的政綱</span>簡介  推動建制派 支持警察 違法違憲 加入美國製裁的名單<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我的政綱</span></span>簡介  推動建制派 支持警察 違法違憲 加入美國 歐洲 加拿大製裁的名單<br />\n  <br />\n1.中國和特區政府 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">『釐清』</span></span>是否需要遵守中英聯合聲明《基本法》『立法會議事規則』及『香港法律』或 中英聯合聲明 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經終止條約</span></span><br />\n <span style=\"color: gold;\"></span><br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港真正最重要是『行政』『立法』《管治權》爭奪戰</span></span>   實現<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">200萬市民 訴求 真雙普選</span></span>策略和行動的《目標》路線圖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重建敗壞</span></span>行政、立法、司法、香港制度<br />\n                             <br />\n3. 五大訴求香港人爭取實現路線圖<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">行使抵觸</span></span>《基本法》《緊急法》</span></span>[/red]<br />\n  <br />\n4. 要求根據 第427章 《刑事罪行(酷刑)條例》犯法公務員作出起訴<br />\n「酷刑罪」是指公職人員在執行公務時，蓄意使他人受到劇烈疼痛或痛苦，最高刑罰為終身監禁，但檢控必須取得律政司司長同意。</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尋找 提名人/義工<br />\n代號 G19 黃埔東<br />\n支持我狙擊梁麗芬的選區 候選人</span></span></div></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持我</span></span>狙擊殺人傀儡梁麗芬 《拗著數》 《發假誓》 《法律界敗類》 賣港 投共</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"08e096bae670450dcfaed0c70d5b65f3ab1113c4","tid":1654324,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"[整合]國際戰線三籌款，一齊捐爆佢！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"594a69da18797492d92eb6414f0d3fccdc357877","tid":1654324,"uid":34470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"字又打錯 個區本身又有人出<br />\n想界票？屌你老母<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"1e10b4af7c6b1062fdb6995a40655bc47c1827b6","tid":1654324,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf453b162940ca5cc0a79eaac69a1c8efd830dc8","tid":1654324,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594a69da18797492d92eb6414f0d3fccdc357877","tid":1654324,"uid":34470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"字又打錯 個區本身又有人出<br />\n想界票？屌你老母<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T20:47:21.000Z","msg":"一齊實現《五大訴求》[《真實雙普選》路線圖 反對《緊急法》<br />\n<br />\n你支持這些拗著數的正棍， 他們是否懂得什麼是緊急法<br />\n，比送中條例也更厲害 ，不懂得宣傳 ，要反對這個違憲的法律 ，出嚟淨係想拗著數 ，投共產黨啦 ，唔好扮做香港人，淨係識得小圈子分贓政治.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你知唔知道現在死咗幾多人?<br />\n幾多人受傷?<br />\n幾多人拘捕?<br />\n將來更加會拘捕多少人?<br />\n你還有沒有良心? <br />\n你對得住這些死難者和拘捕的人是嗎？</span></span>"}]}